Can the Cleveland Cavaliers defend at a championship level? Tom Haberstroh last week listed this as one of his five burning questions for the season, and it's one that we'll be revisiting as the 2014-15 campaign unfolds. The Cavs have played just twice heading into Tuesday's road matchup with the Portland Trail Blazers, so it's far too early to know the answer to the question. We are, however, starting to get an idea of how new coach Dave Blatt is going to try to get there.